2. The 22nd day of August 2024 is appointed as the day on which the Control 

of Exports Act 2023 (No. 27 of 2023) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my hand, 
 21 August 2024 

DARA CALLEARY TD 
 Minister of State for Trade Promotion, Digital and 

Company Regulation. Department of Enterprise, 
Trade and Employment. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 23rd August, 2024.
